      "content": "That's a good start for the core tenets, but it's a bit brief for a high school level debate. Can you expand on the \"strains public resources\" part? I want them to have specific logical links—like how it affects local infrastructure, education, or the economy—so they can't just dismiss it as a vague claim. Could you flesh that out a bit?",
